N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 1 ยง 111.17 - Seed records

State Regulations

Possessors of certified seed will maintain careful
records from which the following data can be determined: (a) Amounts of seed held; listed by species, certification number, and date of acquisition. (b) Amounts of seed disposed of during
previous year; listed by species, certification number, date of sale, and name
of person receiving it. Notes
